.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Iustus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/23/01 9:18:09 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> War Sunday 4pm est on Tarew Marr</span><hr size=1> I know some of you read here, so I am reposting here. Follow this link for details:<br>
