-Iustus <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utyknee.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tyknee</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(5/23/01 10:44:40 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Coldain Hero's Insignia Ring **NEW THREAD**</span><hr size=1> First, great work and thanks to those brave enough to blaze the path for the rest of us.<br>
